Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.15,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.55,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In search of the magic stone, Asta and the \Nothers arrived at the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:43.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,where they were forced to participate in High\NPriest Gifso's game, the Temple Battle Royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.69,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,According to your ranking system,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.90,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,my temple mages would be more\Npowerful than intermediate knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.07,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm gonna get discouraged \Njust because I'm surrounded by water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Magna and Luck also participated in the game,\Nhoping to get the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:10.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ya snooze, ya lose, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.51,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.18,main,Shark Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, aren't you lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.68,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,My son is the strongest mage \Nof the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.29,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:30.56,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it... He's definitely \Nthe strongest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.53,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,You two should come at me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.78,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not hurt you \Nany more than I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.87,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.19,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't ending anyone, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:44.85,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done having fun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who appeared \Nbefore Magna and Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:55.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was one of the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun's top brass, Vetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:03.43,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.67,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}The Pointlessly Direct Fireball\Nand the Wild Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.57,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:56.36,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Asta is looking up \Nat the same moon right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.46,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, silly me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.34,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha? I guess I fell asleepâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.68,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.24,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Not even good for a warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.45,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pack of mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:32.74,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:33.54,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.41,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:59.32,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I know we were all on vacation, but there \Nwere a number of senior Magic Knights here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:04.57,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,And they were all defeated by one guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:09.83,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What were the Magic Knights we \Nbelieved in so much all about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.15,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That thing wasn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.96,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.36,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd this macho dude suddenly come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He looks pretty hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that shark guy was my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:33.57,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is... This guy's magic \Npower is greater than Captain Yami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.10,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,You made it through \Nthe rough ocean currents
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.77,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,and then forced your way in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.11,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,That's some incredible magic, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.99,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I guess you can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.67,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:53.00,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you're not a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.84,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to the Underwater Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:01.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We're after the same thing as those \Ntwo over there, the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.96,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But it's not like I'm \Njust going to hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:10.01,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't expect you to just hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:14.47,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to lay waste to everyone here,\Nmake you despair, and seize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.72,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.44,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter and spread despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.55,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.18,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're all rather rude, abrupt guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.24,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Could you head on home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.74,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.16,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's also a pretty rude \Nway to address someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.03,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:37.79,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,do something about it,\Nand hit me with all your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.81,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're completely \Nunderestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.42,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I am the \Nstrongest in the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Enough talk! Say it with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.05,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.27,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:08.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Rhinoceros Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.61,italics,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even faze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.34,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bad spell, for a mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.62,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.96,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,A reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.13,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a reward called despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,This world is all about the \Nsurvival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.72,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest beasts survive, and the \Nweak vermin live only to become prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.47,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Bear Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:52.86,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a good feel for how \Nvastly different our powers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:58.13,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You insects aren't even \Nallowed to hold on to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:09.13,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:14.08,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The temple's greatest warrior, Gio, \Nis being defeated so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.47,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:23.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gramps. Playtime's over. \NHurry up and get me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:29.11,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist... \NBut who in the world is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:33.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the leaders of a nasty terror \Ngroup called the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.66,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:40.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to explain.\NWe're short on time, so hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.13,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:46.79,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave here until the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:51.80,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even undo the spell. \NThose are the rules of my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:55.47,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just let myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:58.64,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:02.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.90,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.40,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.91,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Different Dimension Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.42,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're trapped in my spatial magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.66,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,no matter who you are,\Nyou won't be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.42,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Black, foreign swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:32.00,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The mana tells me you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.05,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there and watch for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.59,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my main dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:42.60,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,After I season you with despair, \Nas you watch all of your friends die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.64,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets out, the temple's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.38,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it so they hear us out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.95,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:56.86,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.87,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Testing, testing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.66,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,That's the captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.58,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumbasses, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:09.45,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I beat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.83,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someone really dangerous \Njust crashed the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.37,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the leaders of \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:18.37,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and a beast of a man strong enough to go \Nhead-to-head with a Magic Knight Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.39,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:28.76,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, three of his underlings \Nare over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.51,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and hand over \Nthat yummy-looking food...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.70,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the problem... Due to reasons, \NI can't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What do you mean, "reasons"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.44,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you guys gotta \Ndo something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:40.99,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, surpass your limits,\Nright here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.43,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.34,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.00,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:58.68,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the game \Ncould get so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:03.51,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game that'll determine the fate \Nof the Underwater Temple, blast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.10,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The game rules have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.27,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,No time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:13.77,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,To clear the game, defeat the\NEye of the Midnight Sun's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.12,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Those who contribute to clearing the game
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:21.93,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,will get any wish that's \Nwithin my power to grant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's an absolute monster here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.75,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That makes him worth fighting even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:40.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this... I'm gonna do this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.18,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.97,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to put \Nour match on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.52,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:57.24,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Who's my next prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.30,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could move on to the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.08,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're still alive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:18.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,After what Mister Yami said, \NI can't just lie here napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.05,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.77,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.45,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:34.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The more stubborn the prey, the better \Nit is when they're finally in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.05,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we managed to get back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.88,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,but how the hell are we supposed \Nto fight that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:57.24,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If he lands even one more decent \Nblow on us, we're finished... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.42,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.88,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hit us with another one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That really fast one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.57,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Luck! What the hell?! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:11.14,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We just barely managed to block that attack, \Nand we both still took a ton of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.39,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're imitating me. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.02,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep giving you despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.05,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,until you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:32.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I thought! That spell leaves a \Nsplit-second opening right after you attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So you're already matching my pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.75,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good speed and sharp \Nsenses, I'll give you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.42,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My Thunderbolt Destruction \Ndidn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.67,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.47,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You speedy little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:38.52,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That battle maniac... Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.52,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Magna, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.81,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.80,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luck. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:53.28,flashbackitalics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the guy who's called the Smiling\NCombat Fiend and Luck the Cheery Berserker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.54,flashbackitalics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I need to show him who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:15:00.12,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.46,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:04.46,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:10.84,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I joined the squad, he was an \Nannoying pest who messed with me constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.51,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,His personality was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.13,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,"This dude's got some serious issues."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.30,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.17,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.01,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.44,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Even on our missions,\Nhe would do insane things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.29,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.32,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.81,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.90,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to admit that \Nhe has great battle instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:57.22,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And since that dungeon mission, \Nhe's gotten even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.39,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it,\Nbut you're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.19,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare leave me behind, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:17.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Grand Slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.75,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crush it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.85,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.35,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you, I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.56,flashbackitalics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A peasant, huh? He looks boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.32,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But my instincts warned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:54.61,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They told me, "This guy's gonna \Nbe dangerous, yet interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.37,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You interested me so much \Nthat I kept messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.37,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That pudding you were \Nsaving sure was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.16,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be your last supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:09.38,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You always struck back at \Nme with everything you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.30,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I just now realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.63,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,that you're my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.10,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.65,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That you're my very first friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:26.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! I bet you've got even more in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.86,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.29,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch, Fireball Gangster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a gangster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me, Lightning Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.50,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough playtime, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're just about warmed up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:56.14,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell when you \Ncan't even sense mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense mana, but I can sense ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.44,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Ki? It's true that I sense a \Nstrong magical power up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:05.05,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,And it's incredibly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.56,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt anything like it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.31,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But as you said, we've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your ki earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:18.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to sense your presence.\NHow were you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:24.83,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by dancing, I unconsciously \Nput myself into a trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A trance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.03,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm in that state, my body moves \Nwithout me even having to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.84,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Then my opponents can't predict my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's actually possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.65,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Putting myself into a trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.77,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a clear view of that magic now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.35,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Flame and lightning magic are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Flame and lightning... \NIt must be Magna and Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.57,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Their opponent has huge magic and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.19,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.03,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,It's like hundreds of raging beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:06.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Vetto! Wait, you can tell all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:10.33,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,My tribe's eyes are good at picking up magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.92,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is who we're up against...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:18.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are crazy, but when it comes \Ndown to it, they're both super reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.79,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you finally get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:35.44,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The weak get eaten, and all \Nthey have left is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Like we have time for that, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.20,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,If we were in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:51.43,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be too embarrassed to \Nact like his superiors again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.96,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.85,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.60,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.98,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,that if we fight him normally,\Nwe probably won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.69,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.03,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.11,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That slight opening we have \Nright after he attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.54,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.04,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hit him with all the magic we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.87,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,A simultaneous, full-power, body \Nand soul attack at close range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.17,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they were trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Magna... Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This power is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:21:00.65,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Magic: Flame Lightning \NExplosive Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:09.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:54.35,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:53.29,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:57.85,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:00.24,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:03.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hear you! Put a little \Nmore umph into it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:08.65,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're going to show you how you can \Ndo an easy Crackling Magna Typhoon at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.50,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,First, have a string of lightning ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:12.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No one can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.52,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you wrap that lightning \Nstring around Magna, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's electrocuting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:18.97,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll have to get your own Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:20.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do that, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Once you wrap the lightning \Nstring around him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to spin him with \Nall your strength like a top.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the Crackling Magna Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:30.62,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:33.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can do this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:37.01,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up, no matter \Nhow powerful my enemy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:46.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm... We're the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:49.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 45: " The Guy \NWho Doesn't Know When to Quit."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 45\N\N{\fs18} The Guy Who Doesn't Know When to Quit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:50.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:53.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
